Open Payments API Endpoint Classes

Source: R/S7_open.R
openpayments.Rd

Open Payments API Endpoint Classes

Usage

open_endpoint(alias)

open_group(alias)

open_temporal(alias)

open_troup(alias)

Arguments

alias

<chr> endpoint alias

Value

An S7 <open_endpoint>, <open_group>, <open_temporal>, or <open_troup> object

Examples
